These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-1::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: magic-tricks, fishing, drawing, card-games, singing, dancing, board-games
7 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, dog, ferret, goat, mouse, rat
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 4. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
 6. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
10. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
12. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
13. the person who's hobby is dancing is in the middle##1
14. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
15. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
16. the owner of the goat is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
17. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
18. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7      |
| Nationality   | magic-tricks | card-games | singing | dancing | board-games | drawing | fishing |
| Pet           | ferret   | mouse    | rat       | cat     | dog    | goat   | chinchilla |

