 9. the librarian is somewhere to the right of the coach##5
10. the japanese is on the right of the freelancer##1
11. the freelancer is not the french##6
12. the lawyer is on the far right##1
13. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the coach##5
14. the dressmaker is the malaysian##1
15. the japanese is on the left of the dressmaker##1
16. the librarian is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
17. the french is on the right of the dressmaker##1
18. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the coach##5
19. the coach is on the right of the scientist##1
20. the entrepreneur is on the right of the freelancer##1
21. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5

