The people have 7 different jobs:  coach, entrepreneur, journalist, lawyer, manager, security-guard, videographer
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, coffee, iced-tea, sprite
 1. the coach is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the videographer##5
 3. the person drinking sprite is not the journalist##6
 4. the videographer is on the left or right of the manager##3
 5. the lawyer is on the left of the coach##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
 7. the journalist is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 8. the journalist is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking sprite##2
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
10. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the videographer##5
11. the person drinking coffee is between the security-guard and the videographer##2
12. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
13. the lawyer is somewhere to the left of the manager##5
14. the person drinking tea is the videographer##1
15. the manager is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
16. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
17. the coach is on the right of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |     4      |      5       |    6    |       7        |
| Job           | lawyer    | coach     | entrepreneur | journalist | videographer | manager | security-guard |
| Nationality   | iced-tea | hot-chocolate | sprite     | almond-milk   | tea      | coffee  | fanta      |

