 1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the person who's hobby is photography##6
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking mirinda##2
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the person who's hobby is skydiving##6
12. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
13. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
14. the person who's hobby is hiking is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
15. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3

