.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-20::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: indie, gospel, dubstep, house, jazz, hip-hop, folk
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, fishing, puzzles, reading, singing, skydiving, video-games
 1. the fan folk is on the left or right of the fan dubstep##3
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is not the fan hip-hop##6
 3. the fan indie is between the person who's hobby is camping and the fan gospel##2
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 6. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the fan jazz##5
 8. the fan jazz is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the fan dubstep is somewhere to the left of the fan gospel##5
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the fan gospel##1
11. the fan folk is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
12. the fan folk is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
13. the fan jazz is on the left of the fan house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3    |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | dubstep | folk   | gospel  | indie     | jazz | house    | hip-hop |
| Hobby      | skydiving     | reading | puzzles | singing | camping  | video-games | fishing |

 